sequenceDiagram
  participant L as Learner
  participant FE as Next.js
  participant API as .NET API
  participant Hub as ConversationHub
  participant ASR as Whisper
  participant LLM as Anthropic Haiku 4.5
  participant TTS as ElevenLabs

  L->>FE: /speaking/sessions/{id}/warmup
  FE->>API: POST start-warmup
  API-->>FE: 200
  L->>Hub: connect (SignalR)
  Hub-->>L: warm-up persona seeded
  L->>Hub: audio chunk
  Hub->>ASR: transcribe
  ASR-->>Hub: text
  Hub->>LLM: warm-up turn
  LLM-->>Hub: reply text
  Hub->>TTS: synth
  TTS-->>Hub: audio
  Hub-->>L: audio out
  L->>API: POST finish-warmup
  API-->>FE: 200 (state=Prep)
  FE->>L: redirect /prep
  L->>API: POST start-roleplay
  API-->>FE: 200 (state=Active)
  Note over L,TTS: per-turn loop (persona cached)
  L->>API: POST end
  API->>API: enqueue SpeakingAiAssessmentService
  API-->>Hub: AssessmentReady
  Hub-->>L: redirect /results
